{"id":646749,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/【草泥马语】正确的集体记忆/","date":"2020-06-10T01:39:07Z","modified":"2020-06-10T01:39:07Z","title":"【草泥马语】正确的集体记忆","content":"<p>2020年6月8日，外交部发言人办公室发微博报道，中国国务院新闻办公室发表关于《抗击新冠肺炎疫情的中国行动》白皮书，华春莹评论：“中方发表白皮书绝不是为了辩护，而是为了记录。因为抗疫叙事不能被谎言误导玷污，而应留下正确的人类集体记忆。”</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-646684 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/正确集体记忆.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"379\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/正确集体记忆.png 1192w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/正确集体记忆-300x228.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/正确集体记忆-1024x777.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/正确集体记忆-768x582.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/正确集体记忆-1080x819.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646750\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"220\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-6.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-6-300x132.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>微博网友对此进行嘲讽：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646751\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/屏幕快照-2020-06-09-下午9.33.46.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/屏幕快照-2020-06-09-下午9.33.46.png 587w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/屏幕快照-2020-06-09-下午9.33.46-300x248.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646752\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/屏幕快照-2020-06-09-下午9.34.01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"119\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/屏幕快照-2020-06-09-下午9.34.01.png 678w, htt